{"about_the_game":"Step back into the unsettling world of <i>Mr. Hopp's Playhouse</i> where every child's nightmare becomes a chilling reality in this stylized remake. Play as Ruby, a young girl haunted by her toy rabbit <i>Mr. Hopp</i>, gifted to her by her late grandmother. When Ruby discovers that Mr. Hopp has vanished from his usual spot and transformed into a terrifying monster, the night takes a sinister turn, plunging Ruby into a heart-pounding quest to evade the malevolent toy's pursuit.<br><br>Navigate Ruby's perilous path through the house, tiptoeing past scattered toys and obstacles while evading Mr. Hopp's relentless search. With each step fraught with danger, players must carefully strategize their movements, leaping over obstacles to avoid making noise that could give away their location. In this tense 2D sidescroller, survival hinges on quick thinking and stealthy evasion as players race to unravel the mystery surrounding Ruby's haunted companion.<br><br>Will you outwit Mr. Hopp and survive his deadly game of hide-and-seek? Play now and experience the HD remake of the hit indie horror with improved graphics, difficulty settings, unlockable cosmetics and achievements.<br><br>[WASD] - Move<br>[SHIFT] - Run<br>[SPACE] - Jump<br>[E] - Interact<br>[LEFT CLICK] - Shoot<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945990/extras/hopp1hdA.gif?t=1716361723\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945990/extras/hopp1hdB.gif?t=1716361723\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"NOISEMAKER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2945990/13e1e5fe0efa333c5268d2f49e6867fc8f7a5f25.jpg"},{"name":"I AIN'T SCARED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2945990/273721eca952a8c035fb18e029f19063f4e44be6.jpg"},{"name":"BURN, BABY, BURN","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstat